WEBVTT

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:19.000
Alissa
by C. J. MOORE

00:20.000 --> 00:22.000
Alissa is reading.  

00:22.100 --> 00:24.000
Her father calls to her.

00:24.100 --> 00:27.000
Alissa? Alissa?

00:27.500 --> 00:29.000
Alissa runs to the door.

00:29.000 --> 00:31.500
There is a car outside the house.

00:32.000 --> 00:35.000
Her father is talking to a fat man.

00:35.100 --> 00:39.000
"This is Alissa. She reads all day."

00:39.000 --> 00:44.000
Her father says. The two men laugh.

00:44.000 --> 00:47.000
Alissa?

00:47.000 --> 00:52.000
Her father says, "My friend has work for you in the city."

00:52.000 --> 00:58.000
"There isn't any work here in the village. You must go with him."

00:58.000 --> 01:02.000
The fat man smiles at Alissa.

01:02.000 --> 01:04.000
How old are you?

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
He asks.

01:06.000 --> 01:07.000
I'm 12.

01:07.000 --> 01:11.000
She says. The fat man laughs again.

01:11.000 --> 01:16.000
Alissa doesn't like him. She doesn't want to go with this man.

01:16.000 --> 01:19.000
She wants to go to school in the village.

01:19.000 --> 01:23.000
She likes school. She likes reading.

01:23.000 --> 01:26.000
Your mother is packing your things.

01:26.000 --> 01:30.000
You must go to the city, her father says.

01:30.000 --> 01:34.000
The fat man gives some money to Alissa's father.

01:34.000 --> 01:37.000
Alissa's father is pleased and happy.

01:37.000 --> 01:41.000
Alissa is angry and afraid.

01:41.000 --> 01:50.000
Alissa does not want to go with this man, but she must obey her father.

01:50.000 --> 01:54.000
Alissa and the fat man arrive in the city.

01:54.000 --> 01:56.000
They drive to a house.

01:56.000 --> 01:59.000
A thin man comes to the door.

01:59.000 --> 02:01.000
The two men talk.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.000
Here is your room.

02:03.000 --> 02:06.000
The thin man says to Alissa.

02:06.000 --> 02:09.000
He points to a door under the steps.

02:09.000 --> 02:12.000
Alissa goes into the room.

02:12.000 --> 02:15.000
The room is small and dark.

02:15.000 --> 02:18.000
It is her new home.

02:18.000 --> 02:22.000
The next morning, the thin man takes Alissa into the house.

02:22.000 --> 02:24.000
This is Alissa.

02:24.000 --> 02:26.000
The man says to his wife.

02:26.000 --> 02:28.000
She likes reading.

02:28.000 --> 02:30.000
They laugh.

02:30.000 --> 02:33.000
Hahaha.

02:33.000 --> 02:36.000
Suddenly, the woman shouts at Alissa.

02:36.000 --> 02:39.000
You aren't going to read here.

02:39.000 --> 02:40.000
She shouts.

02:40.000 --> 02:44.000
You're going to cook and clean and wash.

02:44.000 --> 02:48.000
Alissa works 15 hours a day.

02:48.000 --> 02:51.000
The woman shouts at her every day.

02:51.000 --> 02:53.000
Alissa is very unhappy.

02:53.000 --> 02:58.000
She cries every night.

02:58.000 --> 03:01.000
One day, the thin man says to Alissa.

03:01.000 --> 03:03.000
Pack your things.

03:03.000 --> 03:05.000
You must go.

03:05.000 --> 03:07.000
My wife doesn't like you.

03:07.000 --> 03:11.000
The thin man takes her to a clothes shop in the city.

03:11.000 --> 03:14.000
The shop owner is a large woman.

03:14.000 --> 03:17.000
She gives the man some money.

03:17.000 --> 03:19.000
He goes away.

03:19.000 --> 03:22.000
He doesn't say goodbye to Alissa.

03:28.000 --> 03:31.000
Alissa works with five other girls.

03:31.000 --> 03:35.000
They work in a small, dark room.

03:35.000 --> 03:38.000
The girls work all day.

03:38.000 --> 03:40.000
They make clothes.

03:40.000 --> 03:43.000
They work 12 hours a day.

03:43.000 --> 03:47.000
At midday, they eat lunch.

03:47.000 --> 03:51.000
After lunch, they rest for 10 minutes.

03:51.000 --> 03:54.000
At night, they sleep on the floor.

03:58.000 --> 04:03.000
Each month, the shop owner gives the girls a little money.

04:03.000 --> 04:07.000
Alissa buys a book with her money.

04:07.000 --> 04:10.000
She reads the book after lunch.

04:10.000 --> 04:13.000
The shop owner is surprised.

04:13.000 --> 04:16.000
The other girls can't read.

04:16.000 --> 04:18.000
Can you write?

04:18.000 --> 04:20.000
Can you count?

04:20.000 --> 04:22.000
The shop owner asks.

04:22.000 --> 04:24.000
Yes, I can.

04:24.000 --> 04:26.000
Alissa says.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.000
Come.

04:27.000 --> 04:30.000
The shop owner says.

04:30.000 --> 04:33.000
You are going to work in the shop.

04:37.000 --> 04:40.000
Alissa likes working in the shop.

04:40.000 --> 04:43.000
She serves the customers.

04:43.000 --> 04:46.000
The customers are rich ladies.

04:46.000 --> 04:50.000
They buy expensive dresses.

04:50.000 --> 04:54.000
One of the customers is a tall and pretty lady.

04:54.000 --> 04:58.000
She always smiles at Alissa.

04:58.000 --> 05:01.000
She gives Alissa small presents.

05:02.000 --> 05:07.000
One day, the tall lady leaves her purse in the shop.

05:07.000 --> 05:10.000
Alissa runs out into the street.

05:10.000 --> 05:13.000
She runs after the lady.

05:13.000 --> 05:15.000
Here is your purse.

05:15.000 --> 05:17.000
Alissa says.

05:17.000 --> 05:19.000
The lady smiles.

05:19.000 --> 05:22.000
She takes the money from the purse.

05:22.000 --> 05:23.000
Thank you.

05:23.000 --> 05:25.000
She says to Alissa.

05:25.000 --> 05:28.000
You are an honest girl.

05:29.000 --> 05:31.000
Take this money.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.000
No.

05:32.000 --> 05:33.000
No.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.000
Says Alissa.

05:34.000 --> 05:36.000
I don't want your money.

05:36.000 --> 05:39.000
She runs back to the shop.

05:39.000 --> 05:42.000
The shop owner shouts at her.

05:42.000 --> 05:44.000
Don't leave the shop again.

05:44.000 --> 05:45.000
She shouts.

05:45.000 --> 05:47.000
I pay you a lot of money.

05:47.000 --> 05:49.000
I pay you to work.

05:49.000 --> 05:52.000
I don't pay you to run out into the street.

05:53.000 --> 05:55.000
Alissa is angry.

05:55.000 --> 05:58.000
You don't pay me a lot of money.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.000
She shouts.

05:59.000 --> 06:01.000
I'm a slave here.

06:01.000 --> 06:03.000
You're an ungrateful girl.

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
The large woman says.

06:05.000 --> 06:08.000
You have a bed and food and money.

06:08.000 --> 06:10.000
Do you want more?

06:10.000 --> 06:12.000
Yes, I do.

06:12.000 --> 06:13.000
Alissa says.

06:13.000 --> 06:15.000
She is crying now.

06:15.000 --> 06:17.000
Wait.

06:17.000 --> 06:19.000
A quiet voice.

06:20.000 --> 06:21.000
Wait.

06:21.000 --> 06:23.000
A quiet voice says.

06:23.000 --> 06:26.000
The tall lady is standing at the door.

06:26.000 --> 06:29.000
Alissa isn't ungrateful.

06:29.000 --> 06:31.000
The tall lady says.

06:31.000 --> 06:34.000
She is an honest girl.

06:34.000 --> 06:37.000
The tall lady speaks to Alissa.

06:37.000 --> 06:39.000
Aren't you happy here?

06:39.000 --> 06:40.000
She asks.

06:40.000 --> 06:42.000
What do you want?

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
Alissa says.

06:44.000 --> 06:47.000
I want to go to school.

06:50.000 --> 06:53.000
The tall lady turns to the shop owner.

06:53.000 --> 06:56.000
Alissa will live in my house.

06:56.000 --> 06:57.000
She says.

06:57.000 --> 06:59.000
She won't work.

06:59.000 --> 07:01.000
She will go to school.

07:01.000 --> 07:03.000
You must pay me.

07:03.000 --> 07:04.000
The shop owner says.

07:04.000 --> 07:05.000
No.

07:05.000 --> 07:07.000
The tall lady says.

07:07.000 --> 07:10.000
Alissa isn't a slave.

07:10.000 --> 07:12.000
Pack your things, Alissa.

07:12.000 --> 07:13.000
She says.

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
We will go home now.

07:16.000 --> 07:19.000
Alissa goes with the tall lady.

07:19.000 --> 07:22.000
She is going to a new home.

07:22.000 --> 07:25.000
She is going to be happy.
